claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table summarizing clinical trial efficacy of Flublok versus placebo for prevention of PCR- or culture-confirmed influenza-like illness, showing numbers of cases, attack rates, vaccine efficacy percentages (with 95% CIs), broken down by matched strains, any strain, subtypes A and B. The image presents efficacy data against influenza-like illness and matched versus any strains but contains no information regarding antigenic matching processes or confirmation of identical antigenic match with WHO- or FDA-selected strains, and thus does not support the claim.
